" A little cleverer (but I think it'll probably cause a headache later):
"nnoremap <cr> :noh<cr>

" Centre search results
nnoremap n nzz
nnoremap N Nzz
nnoremap * *zz
nnoremap # #zz
nnoremap g* g*zz
nnoremap g# g#zz

" Map F10 to open the current folder in netrw (or NERDTree)
